nodes.text: Star Wars Resistance: Complete Season One

Star Wars Resistance: Complete Season One is a DVD compilation of the first season of the animated series Star Wars Resistance. It was released by Buena Vista Home Entertainment, Inc. on August 20, 2019.

Recruited by Poe Dameron for a top secret Resistance mission, hotshot pilot Kazuda "Kaz" Xiono finds himself in over his head when he and BB-8 are stationed aboard a large aircraft refueling station. Join Kaz on this high-flying adventure as he struggles to keep his cover as a mechanic and gets entangled with ace pilots, marauding pirates, villainous stormtroopers, and other colorful characters.
